Telling PHP to display errors:\
\
**We want to show the most errors in a development environment, and suppress errors in a production environment\
\
1. php.ini file\
\
- Find location of php.ini by visiting localhost/dashboard/phpinfo.php and scrolling down to \'93Loaded Configuration File Path.\
- Open in Terminal by typing \'93sudo vi \'93 followed by path. Enter user password\
- May also open in TextEdit\
